i fenomeni e delle forme notevoli 0 arestricted accessuhttp://purl.org/coar/access_right/c_16ecfonline access with authorization2star  aOltre un’introduzione dettagliata al contesto storico-sociale della situazione linguistica in Sardegna, il volume contiene descrizioni sincroniche e diacroniche di tutti i settori dei sistemi linguistici, sia delle varietà sarde in senso stretto che delle varietà alloglotte dell’isola. Questo Manuale costituisce, cioè, un lavoro di riferimento obbligato per chiunque si occupi della lingua e della linguistica sarda.   aThis manual will be an indispensable research tool for everyone interested in the Sardinian language and in Romance linguistics in general. It presents the first extensive overview of the various questions and problems of Sardinian linguistics. In addition to a detailed introduction to the socio-historical background of the current linguistic situation in Sardinia, it provides diachronic and synchronic descriptions both of the varieties of Sardinian itself and of the other idioms spoken on the island.   aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn Italian.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Aug 2020) 0aSardinian languagexSocial aspects. 0aSardinian language. 4aLanguage History. 4aLinguistics. 4aLinguistik. 4aSardinian. 4aSardisch. 4aSprachgeschichte. 4aSprachkontakt. 7aLANGUAGE ARTS & DISCIPLINES / Linguistics / General.2bisacsh1 aBlasco Ferrer, Eduardo, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aKoch, Peter, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aMarzo, Daniela , eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2017z978311071954308iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2017z9783110540550oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PAC